Standard .gitignore file for C++ projects

--- Build Artifacts ---

*.o        # Object files
*.a        # Static libraries
*.so       # Dynamic libraries (Linux)
*.dll      # Dynamic libraries (Windows)
*.exe      # Executable files (Windows)
a.out      # Default executable name (Linux/macOS)
*.dSYM/    # Debug symbols (macOS)
/bin/      # Common folder for final binaries
/build/    # Common folder for build output

--- Operating System Files ---

.DS_Store  # macOS metadata files
Thumbs.db  # Windows metadata files

--- IDE/Editor Files ---

.vscode/

Ignore settings specific to some IDEs

.idea/     # IntelliJ / CLion / JetBrains
*.sublime-workspace
*.sublime-project